commentTextItems.html: and the change works instantly as Dockrell wraps it up by clean bowling Raja with a nicely flighted delivery. Ireland win 70 runs.

commentPostTextItems.html: So the Netherlands are all out for 205 in an innings played almost constantly in drizzle. Gary Wilson's fabulous century was the highlight and the Netherlands never looked like they would be able to chase the target down.
The two teams face each other on Wednesday so do join us again for that but for now from a rainy Dublin it's goodbye.
